form.current-chamber: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES
form.official-title: Providing for a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 3547.

section.text: That in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 3547, the Clerk of the House of Representatives shall amend the long title so as to read: Making consolidated appropriations for the fiscal year ending September 30, 2014, and for other purposes..

attestation-group.attestation-date: Passed the House of Representatives January 15, 2014.
